Single-database Alembic configuration for Merbana backend.

Migration policy:
- Use Alembic revisions for all schema changes.
- Do not manually alter SQLite schema.
- Review autogenerated migrations before applying.

Environment variable:
- MERBANA_DB_URL: SQLAlchemy DB URL for migration commands.

Examples:
- Linux/macOS: MERBANA_DB_URL='sqlite:////abs/path/merbana.db' python -m alembic -c Deployment/backend/alembic.ini upgrade head
- Windows PowerShell: $env:MERBANA_DB_URL='sqlite:///C:/path/to/merbana.db'; python -m alembic -c Deployment/backend/alembic.ini upgrade head
